I was sitting here.

81
00:05:07,660 --> 00:05:11,760
The wind blew dust into my eyes. That's why I'm crying.

82
00:05:13,840 --> 00:05:16,500
Tears wash the dust out of your eyes.

83
00:05:16,500 --> 00:05:22,520
