187
00:12:03,560 --> 00:12:05,560
But you just said you wanted to be alone.

188
00:12:05,560 --> 00:12:08,420
Now you're saying it's good to have me around.

189
00:12:08,420 --> 00:12:10,760
What exactly do you want?

190
00:12:14,440 --> 00:12:16,850
If one day...

191
00:12:16,850 --> 00:12:21,820
I make you angry or sad,

192
00:12:24,940 --> 00:12:26,580
will you leave me?

193
00:12:26,580 --> 00:12:30,760
If you know it will make me angry,

194
00:12:30,760 --> 00:12:32,960
why would you do it?

195
00:12:41,440 --> 00:12:43,340
Hey, you.

196
00:12:45,940 --> 00:12:47,980
I used to be alone, too.

197
00:12:47,980 --> 00:12:50,500
But it's not because I liked it.

198
00:12:50,500 --> 00:12:52,960
It's because no one needed me.

199
00:12:52,960 --> 00:12:55,140
People kicked me out of their lives.

200
00:12:55,140 --> 00:12:58,580
But one day, I met you,

201
00:12:58,580 --> 00:13:01,000
a good friend.

202
00:13:01,000 --> 00:13:03,340
If you make me angry one day,

203
00:13:03,340 --> 00:13:05,130
I may...

204
00:13:06,650 --> 00:13:08,920
not kick you out,

205
00:13:08,920 --> 00:13:12,040
because I don't want to lose a good friend like you.

206
00:13:12,040 --> 00:13:13,420
Are you serious?

207
00:13:13,420 --> 00:13:16,240
If that day comes,

208
00:13:16,240 --> 00:13:18,180
you won't be angry at me?

209
00:13:19,760 --> 00:13:22,820
If you have a good reason,

210
00:13:22,820 --> 00:13:27,380
maybe I won't be angry at you.

211
00:13:28,680 --> 00:13:30,460
Pinky swear.

212
00:13:55,940 --> 00:13:59,740
Khun Sira, there's a budget document for the promotion that needs your signature.

213
00:13:59,740 --> 00:14:01,313
Give it to me.

214
00:14:05,486 --> 00:14:09,960
Maha, help me get some documents from Rossarin.

215
00:14:10,840 --> 00:14:14,240
I'll tell Khun Kheetika to get them.

216
00:14:14,240 --> 00:14:16,820
Can't you go and get them for me?

217
00:14:17,640 --> 00:14:21,720
