219
00:14:23,700 --> 00:14:26,140
Are you still angry at Khun Rossarin?

220
00:14:26,140 --> 00:14:28,080
You have been fighting a lot lately.

221
00:14:28,080 --> 00:14:30,060
I didn't do anything.

222
00:14:30,060 --> 00:14:34,480
