229
00:14:52,760 --> 00:14:55,260
But Khun Rossarin didn't seem to find it funny.

230
00:14:56,640 --> 00:15:01,140
I don't know what's wrong between you and Khun Rossarin.

231
00:15:01,140 --> 00:15:04,760
But I know Khun Rossarin has always cared about you.

232
00:15:04,760 --> 00:15:08,120
No matter when you have a problem or when you are sad,

233
00:15:08,120 --> 00:15:09,860
she has always been there for you.

234
00:15:09,860 --> 00:15:12,000
She has never abandoned you.

235
00:15:13,260 --> 00:15:17,560
I don't want you to lose a close friend like Khun Rossarin.

236
