237
00:15:27,700 --> 00:15:30,940
About clothing and accessories,

238
00:15:30,940 --> 00:15:33,220
we will focus on simple colors and incorporate fashion elements from the 1990s

239
00:15:33,220 --> 00:15:35,520
to cater to customers aged 30 to 40.

240
00:15:35,520 --> 00:15:38,420
