516
00:39:12,120 --> 00:39:14,500
I want to hire them to help me find the shoe.

517
00:39:14,500 --> 00:39:16,000
I think they've all gone home.

518
00:39:16,000 --> 00:39:19,920
I'll help you. But we should hurry.

519
00:39:19,920 --> 00:39:24,120
The garbage truck will be collecting garbage in half an hour.

520
00:39:52,740 --> 00:39:57,880
[Kheetika: I'm home.]

