00:40:34,400 --> 00:40:36,800
Mom, I'm scared.

522
00:40:36,800 --> 00:40:39,870
Mom, help me.

523
00:40:39,870 --> 00:40:42,160
Khun Sira, what's wrong?

524
00:40:49,820 --> 00:40:51,160
Help.

525
00:40:51,160 --> 00:40:54,120
Come on, hurry.

526
00:40:54,120 --> 00:40:55,480
- Come with me.
- What's wrong, Madam?

527
00:40:55,480 --> 00:40:56,920
I don't know what's wrong with Khun Sira.

528
00:40:56,920 --> 00:40:58,640
Khun Sira.

529
00:41:03,440 --> 00:41:05,620
[Nannam]

530
00:41:11,500 --> 00:41:13,500
Nannam.

531
00:41:14,672 --> 00:41:18,460
What? What happened to Khun Sira?

532
00:41:20,270 --> 00:41:22,230
Help me.

533
00:41:22,232 --> 00:41:25,980
Khun Sira. Excuse me.

534
00:41:25,980 --> 00:41:28,120
Khun Sira, what happened?

535
00:41:28,120 --> 00:41:30,600
Mom, help me.

536
00:41:30,600 --> 00:41:33,320
Help me.

537
00:41:44,620 --> 00:41:47,320
Help me.

538
00:42:03,898 --> 00:42:07,980
I think Khun Sira saw something

539
00:42:07,980 --> 00:42:10,500
that reminded him of the past.

540
00:42:10,500 --> 00:42:13,980
P'Sira must have had a bad past.

541
00:42:13,980 --> 00:42:18,440
