547
00:42:32,880 --> 00:42:35,325
- Please take care of him.
- Okay.

548
00:42:49,400 --> 00:42:51,080
Done.

549
00:43:15,093 --> 00:43:16,880
Shoe.

550
00:43:37,286 --> 00:43:39,460
Khun Sira.

551
00:43:39,460 --> 00:43:41,900
Where are you going?

552
00:43:41,900 --> 00:43:43,400
I...

553
00:43:44,306 --> 00:43:46,540
I'm going to get your shoe back.

554
00:43:46,540 --> 00:43:49,260
No need. I found it.

555
00:43:49,260 --> 00:43:50,780
I'm sorry.

556
00:43:50,780 --> 00:43:55,040
I didn't mean to throw your shoe away.

557
00:43:55,040 --> 00:43:56,480
It was an accident.

558
00:43:56,480 --> 00:43:58,940
The janitor already told me.

559
00:43:59,920 --> 00:44:03,080
Why don't you go and take a shower?

560
00:44:03,080 --> 00:44:06,440
Then you can have your meal and take your medicine.

561
00:44:07,633 --> 00:44:09,298
You're...

562
00:44:10,340 --> 00:44:13,120
You're not mad at me, are you?

563
00:44:13,120 --> 00:44:14,500
I'm not.

564
00:44:14,500 --> 00:44:20,560
I should thank you for trying to find my shoe.

565
00:44:20,560 --> 00:44:22,799
I'm sorry it made you like this.

566
00:44:23,920 --> 00:44:25,720
Thank you.

567
00:44:33,193 --> 00:44:34,560
However...

568
00:44:40,700 --> 00:44:43,380
Did you pull out the needle yourself?

569
00:44:43,380 --> 00:44:45,700
It's bleeding.

570
00:44:51,700 --> 00:44:56,000
I'll help you change the gauze when you're done eating.

571
00:44:56,000 --> 00:44:57,420
It's all right.

572
00:44:57,420 --> 00:45:00,340
I didn't wet it in the shower.

573
00:45:04,600 --> 00:45:08,900
We don't have any meetings today.

574
00:45:10,240 --> 00:45:12,820
Take a day off at home.

575
00:45:12,820 --> 00:45:15,440
I'm all right now.

576
00:45:15,440 --> 00:45:18,080
I'm fine. I can go to work.

577
00:45:18,080 --> 00:45:21,940
Thank you for saving me last night.

578
00:45:25,800 --> 00:45:30,000
But don't do it again.

579
00:45:30,925 --> 00:45:32,800
Because...

580
00:45:34,232 --> 00:45:37,260
you love those shoes, don't you?

581
00:45:37,260 --> 00:45:39,320
Din bought them for you.

582
00:45:40,120 --> 00:45:43,280
If I lose my shoes, I can buy new ones.

583
00:45:43,280 --> 00:45:46,120
What should I do if something happens to you?

584
00:45:54,000 --> 00:45:55,600
Are you worried about me?

585
00:46:01,946 --> 00:46:03,679
Yes, I'm worried about you.

586
00:46:04,360 --> 00:46:06,900
Because I don't know how to explain to people

587
00:46:06,900 --> 00:46:10,600
that a GU executive died next to a garbage dump.

588
00:46:14,020 --> 00:46:17,120
You don't have to tell the truth.

589
00:46:22,626 --> 00:46:24,400
I can't eat more.

590
00:46:26,047 --> 00:46:27,599
Let me clean it up for you.

591
00:46:27,599 --> 00:46:31,080
It's okay. I can do it myself. You can eat your meal.

592
00:46:31,080 --> 00:46:34,090
It's okay. Let me do it.

593
00:46:35,520 --> 00:46:37,660
It's all dirty.

594
00:46:37,660 --> 00:46:39,360
Go wash your hands.

595
00:46:39,360 --> 00:46:42,440
It's just porridge. What's the fuss?

596
00:46:42,440 --> 00:46:44,920
Dr. Zhao asked me to keep an eye on you.

597
00:46:44,920 --> 00:46:49,320
You're not allowed to touch dirty stuff. Otherwise, you will have a relapse.

598
00:46:49,320 --> 00:46:52,080
I don't want you to be like last night.

599
00:46:58,992 --> 00:47:00,720
Give me your hand.

600
00:47:06,100 --> 00:47:08,440
Okay, it's done.

601
00:47:08,440 --> 00:47:10,980
I don't think it's clean.

602
00:47:10,980 --> 00:47:16,700
If you want to wash my hands, follow the seven-step hand-washing method.

603
00:47:18,000 --> 00:47:19,760
What if I relapse?

604
00:47:19,760 --> 00:47:20,780
How do you do it?

605
00:47:20,780 --> 00:47:27,895
First step, wash your hands like this.

606
00:47:27,895 --> 00:47:31,160
♫ The more you try to flee, the more I want to find you ♫

607
00:47:32,020 --> 00:47:37,060
♫ Not being suspicious, not being careful, suddenly it's stuck in my mind ♫

608
00:47:37,060 --> 00:47:41,620
♫ Are you the one my heart is searching for? ♫

609
00:47:41,620 --> 00:47:46,700
♫ Not wanting to remember, but I can't forget because I miss you ♫

610
00:47:46,700 --> 00:47:50,520
♫ So I have to find you to devote myself to you ♫

611
00:47:50,520 --> 00:47:55,400
♫ I didn't think that I would love you, so I let you go ♫

612
00:47:55,400 --> 00:47:59,600
♫ In the end, I fell madly in love ♫

613
00:47:59,600 --> 00:48:04,400
♫ I don't understand why my heart trembles when I see you ♫

614
00:48:04,400 --> 00:48:09,220
♫ In my dreams, at night and during the day, why do I still long for you? ♫

615
00:48:09,220 --> 00:48:15,860
♫ I can't stop my heart beating out of rhythm like a delirious person ♫

616
00:48:15,860 --> 00:48:18,240
♫ I've really fallen in love with you ♫

617
00:48:18,240 --> 00:48:22,240
♫ The more you try to flee, the more I want to find you ♫

618
00:48:28,820 --> 00:48:32,300
Khun Hom, here's your favorite fish porridge for breakfast.

619
00:48:32,300 --> 00:48:34,520
Come and eat with us.

620
00:48:36,260 --> 00:48:38,240
Dad,

621
00:48:38,240 --> 00:48:43,200
Khun Tongwon has agreed to renew the contract.

622
00:48:47,380 --> 00:48:50,960
I'll send the renewed contract to him later.

623
00:48:50,960 --> 00:48:54,627
If there's no problem, he will sign it.

624
00:48:58,060 --> 00:49:01,320
Dear, I'm full. I'm going to work.

625
00:49:01,320 --> 00:49:03,400
Wait.

626
00:49:03,400 --> 00:49:07,100
It's still early. Eat some fruit.

627
00:49:07,100 --> 00:49:09,200
I'll get it for you.

628
00:49:20,100 --> 00:49:23,880
Dad, when will you stop being angry at me?

629
00:49:23,880 --> 00:49:26,560
You've never been angry at me for so long.

630
00:49:26,560 --> 00:49:28,020
I'm not angry at you.

631
00:49:28,020 --> 00:49:32,600
If you're not angry at me, why won't you talk to me?

632
00:49:32,600 --> 00:49:34,540
Because I feel guilty.

633
00:49:34,540 --> 00:49:39,300
When I see your face, I think of your mother

634
00:49:39,300 --> 00:49:42,500
and my vows to her.

635
00:49:42,500 --> 00:49:44,900
I told her that I would take good care of you

636
00:49:44,900 --> 00:49:47,820
and raise you to be a good person.

637
00:49:47,820 --> 00:49:50,000
But eventually, I failed.

638
00:49:50,000 --> 00:49:55,440
And I almost made you a murderer.

639
00:49:55,440 --> 00:49:57,233
Dad.

640
00:49:59,000 --> 00:50:01,860
You're my only daughter.

641
00:50:01,860 --> 00:50:04,159
But I didn't take good care of you.

642
00:50:04,159 --> 00:50:06,220
Is it because of Kanghan?

643
00:50:06,220 --> 00:50:10,513
I didn't intend to drive into her and kill her.

644
00:50:10,513 --> 00:50:14,027
Why didn't you tell me about that?

645
00:50:25,552 --> 00:50:27,700
I didn't want to hide it from you.

646
00:50:27,700 --> 00:50:31,240
I didn't know how to explain it.

647
00:50:32,618 --> 00:50:34,500
I understand.

648
00:50:34,500 --> 00:50:36,580
Hom is your daughter.

649
00:50:36,580 --> 00:50:40,080
It should be difficult for you to tell me about it.

650
00:50:42,205 --> 00:50:44,180
It's my fault.

651
00:50:45,000 --> 00:50:47,820
You should scold me.

652
00:50:47,820 --> 00:50:50,245
It has nothing to do with my dad.

653
00:50:50,245 --> 00:50:55,700
Then tell me the truth.

654
00:50:55,700 --> 00:50:58,520
Have you ever thought about hitting Kanghan?

655
00:50:58,520 --> 00:51:01,000
I've never thought of it.

656
00:51:01,000 --> 00:51:02,620
Then, why did you do that?

657
00:51:02,620 --> 00:51:05,140
I just wanted to scare Kanghan.

658
00:51:05,140 --> 00:51:08,060
I'm telling the truth.

659
00:51:08,060 --> 00:51:10,280
Believe it or not.

660
00:51:10,280 --> 00:51:12,120
I trust you.

661
00:51:12,788 --> 00:51:16,600
I chose to trust you because you're Papop's daughter.

662
00:51:17,600 --> 00:51:20,703
Papop is a good person.

663
00:51:20,703 --> 00:51:22,980
I'm sure he'll educate you to be a good person,

664
00:51:22,980 --> 00:51:25,840
and he will not teach you to kill.

665
00:51:25,840 --> 00:51:29,580
Khun Hom, you should come to your senses.

666
00:51:29,580 --> 00:51:33,320
Your dad loves you and has high hopes for you.

667
00:51:34,245 --> 00:51:37,580
You should know what to do

668
00:51:37,580 --> 00:51:40,300
so that your dad doesn't worry about you.

669
00:51:42,580 --> 00:51:45,860
I hope this is the last time...

670
00:51:46,840 --> 00:51:49,840
you want to hurt Kanghan.

671
00:51:51,380 --> 00:51:53,920
If you want to hurt her again,

672
00:51:55,760 --> 00:51:58,120
