679
00:52:56,740 --> 00:53:01,680
Ms. Kanghan lives in this apartment? I don't know.

680
00:53:01,700 --> 00:53:03,760
Are you sure?

681
00:53:03,760 --> 00:53:05,540
Yes.

682
00:53:10,906 --> 00:53:16,266
What did Kanghan ask you to hide for her?

683
00:53:28,853 --> 00:53:30,500
Mom.

684
00:53:35,680 --> 00:53:37,460
Brother, are you going back?

685
00:53:40,700 --> 00:53:42,472
What's wrong?

686
00:53:42,472 --> 00:53:45,880
How can you drive home with injured hands?

687
00:53:45,880 --> 00:53:47,480
I'll drive you home.

688
00:53:47,480 --> 00:53:49,980
I can drive by myself.

689
00:53:49,980 --> 00:53:52,100
It's okay.

690
00:53:52,100 --> 00:53:54,520
It's all right, Brother.

691
00:53:56,305 --> 00:54:01,380
What? Don't you want me to drive you home because you have some secrets in your house?

692
00:54:02,513 --> 00:54:04,213
No.

